import './SideNav.scss'; import React from 'react' import {Link,Outlet,useNavigate} from 'react-router-dom' const SideNav = () => { const navigate=useNavigate(); return (
navigate('/Salesparent',{replace: false})}> POS navigate('/WareHouse',{replace:false})}> WareHouse navigate('/Dashboard',{replace:false})}> Dashboard navigate('/Salary',{replace:false})}> Salary
) } export default SideNav;
